## Architecture

This is a multi-platform monorepo containing:

{% if "backend" in platforms %}- **backend/** - Spring Boot 4 (Kotlin) REST API -> Azure Container Apps
{% endif %}{% if "web-user-app" in platforms %}- **web-user-app/** - Next.js user-facing web app (TypeScript) -> Cloudflare via OpenNext
{% endif %}{% if "web-admin-portal" in platforms %}- **web-admin-portal/** - Next.js admin web portal (TypeScript) -> Cloudflare via OpenNext
{% endif %}{% if "mobile-android" in platforms %}- **mobile-android/** - Android app (Kotlin/Jetpack Compose, MVVM)
{% endif %}{% if "mobile-ios" in platforms %}- **mobile-ios/** - iOS app (Swift/SwiftUI, MVVM)
{% endif %}

## First-Time Setup

This project includes a living product wiki at `knowledge/wiki/`. Before building
the first feature, initialize the wiki and advisory board:

- **Claude Code:** `/setup-project`
- **Codex:** `$setup-project`
- **Cursor:** ask the agent to "run setup-project"

This setup step interviews the team about domain risks, creates
`knowledge/wiki/advisory/BOARD.md`, and prepares the wiki for feature intake.

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Set up environment
{% if "backend" in platforms %}cp .env.example .env
{% endif %}{% if "web-user-app" in platforms %}cp web-user-app/.env.example web-user-app/.env.local
{% endif %}{% if "web-admin-portal" in platforms %}cp web-admin-portal/.env.example web-admin-portal/.env.local
{% endif %}
# Edit the copied env files with your {% if "backend" in platforms %}backend{% if "web-user-app" in platforms or "web-admin-portal" in platforms %} and {% endif %}{% endif %}{% if "web-user-app" in platforms or "web-admin-portal" in platforms %}web app{% endif %} credentials

# 2. Generate API clients from OpenAPI spec
task generate-clients
{% if use_docker %}
# 3. Start local services
docker compose up -d
{% endif %}{% if "backend" in platforms %}
# 4. Start backend
task backend:run
{% endif %}{% if "web-user-app" in platforms %}
# 5. Start the user web app
task web-user-app:dev
{% endif %}{% if "web-admin-portal" in platforms %}
# 6. Start the admin web portal
task web-admin-portal:dev
{% endif %}
```

